Version 1rc1 - released 2012-02-11
cmb     updated to CodeMirror 2.38
cmb     changed configuration to be proper JSON
cmb     implemented preview mode (for content editor only)
cmb     added Czech and Slovak localization (contributed by oldnema resp. Tata)
cmb     added German localization and user manual
cmb     cleaned up and improved code
cmb     merged and/or minified JavaScript and CSS files

Version 1beta5 - internally released 2012-12-24
cmb     implemented possibility to use a Codeeditor with an own submit button
cmb     fixed bug, where Codeeditor misbehaved on IE

Version 1beta4 - released 2012-09-03
cmb     updated to CodeMirror 2.33

Version 1beta3 - released 2012-09-02
cmb     fixed bug where external config files were not recognized (reported by svasti)

Version 1beta2 - released 2012-08-24
cmb	updated to CodeMirror 2.22
cmb     implemented editor interface of CMSimple_XH 1.5.2+
cmb     switched to init.js file instead of config options for more flexibility
cmb     implemented additional functionality (available through keyboard shortcuts)
cmb     allowed to save without modifications (suggested by svasti)
cmb     fixed bug: codeeditor didn't work with CMSimple_XH before 1.3
cmb     updated manual

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-01-13
cmb	updated to CodeMirror 2.2
cmb	switched from implicit requirements check to explicit system check
cmb	added several config options
cmb	rewritten without need for jQuery
cmb	implemented editor interface for CMSimple_XH 1.5+
cmb	added default.php for CMSimple_XH 1.5+
cmb	added manual
cmb	cleaned up code
cmb	added warning when leaving page with unsaved modifications (doesn't work in Opera)

Version 1dev1 - released 2011-08-21
cmb	tag()ged <link>s
cmb	added config option: enabled (suggested by Gert)
cmb	fixed: highlighting fails after save
cmb	added fullscreen mode (suggested by Gert)

Version 0.0.2 - released 2011-07-18
cmb	removed console.log() (reported by Gert)

Version 0.0.1 - released 2011-07-18
cmb	initial release